    <article id="main-content" class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="Getting Started with Star Atlas" class="article-title">
          Getting Started with Star Atlas
          
        </h1>

        <div class="article-author">
          
          <div class="article-meta">
            

            <div class="meta-group">
              
                <span class="meta-data"><time datetime="2025-12-08T18:27:16Z" title="2025-12-08T18:27:16Z" data-datetime="relative">December 08, 2025 18:27</time></span>
                <span class="meta-data">Updated</span>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
          <div class="article-subscribe"><div data-helper="subscribe" data-json="{&quot;item&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/hc/en-us/articles/47061455306131-Getting-Started-with-Star-Atlas/subscription.json&quot;,&quot;follow_label&quot;:&quot;Follow&quot;,&quot;unfollow_label&quot;:&quot;Unfollow&quot;,&quot;following_label&quot;:&quot;Following&quot;,&quot;can_subscribe&quot;:true,&quot;is_subscribed&quot;:false}"></div></div>
        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>Star Atlas is a next-gen space metaverse built on the Solana blockchain. Whether you're here to explore, trade, or earn, this guide shows you exactly how to get started, from jumping into the free UE5 game to setting up your fleet in SAGE</p><h3 id="h_01KBJS5TFMAVEQ8FAQWTZ8VMH3">&nbsp;</h3><h3 id="h_01KBZKEQQZE18MT4G333B3XHKZ"><a href="https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/star-atlas-bead34" rel="noopener">Start with the Free-to-Play UE5 Game</a></h3><p>The fastest way to jump into Star Atlas is through the <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/star-atlas-bead34" rel="noopener"><strong>UE5 Game</strong></a>, available on the <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/star-atlas-bead34" rel="noopener"><strong>Epic Games Store</strong></a>. It's free to play, and you don’t need to own any NFTs to start exploring.</p><h4 id="h_01KBJRWBBBRFN3RJBWKV0HXXBQ">What You Can Do:</h4><ul>
<li data-list-item-id="eb3aa1bf991481cf881c39a3c5377cac8">Fly demo ships or your own ships</li>
<li data-list-item-id="e4dbd9cdeb2c254f665b37cfcc8521607">Use crew avatars to explore</li>
<li data-list-item-id="e388a3b5396e629685076d9e00c94ec85">Play solo or multiplayer modes: combat, racing, zone control &amp; more</li>
<li data-list-item-id="ed38c66081128a426771dd69d6afaac84">Mine asteroids in the open world</li>
<li data-list-item-id="e477ab76e2a4a1807ecd121b044560bd0">Race or explore Volant Station, the MUD faction’s central hub</li>
</ul><h4 id="h_01KBJRWBBB68JDDZVW2XRC2CXW">How to Join:</h4><ol>
<li class="ck-list-marker-bold" data-list-item-id="ed15d8e418de2b4dc3f81b8c3416a7693">
<strong>Join the Star Atlas Discord</strong><br><a href="http://discord.gg/staratlas" rel="noopener"><strong>discord.gg/staratlas</strong></a>
</li>
<li class="ck-list-marker-bold" data-list-item-id="e6efa5cd154397dc32b570e45bd80de50">
<strong>Go to the </strong><code><strong>🔑┃game-access-key</strong></code><strong> channel (under “Start Here”)</strong>
</li>
<li class="ck-list-marker-bold" data-list-item-id="e2ec2fb0e15d278fad018285755330049">
<strong>Use the </strong><code><strong>/key</strong></code><strong> command</strong><br><strong>A bot will send you your unique Epic Games key.</strong>
</li>
<li class="ck-list-marker-bold" data-list-item-id="ecd263a78e77dd8ddaf9136425b84ff0e">
<strong>Redeem the Key on Epic Games Launcher</strong><ul>
<li data-list-item-id="e61015b01713110c3968cf7683e5fe9c4">Open Epic Games Launcher</li>
<li data-list-item-id="ea5b64e0da3c9b5f6d2f88d511ff2883d">Log in or create an account</li>
<li data-list-item-id="eec36dd85517f0cc0e331d88b6b352468">Go to your name → "Redeem Code"</li>
<li data-list-item-id="ee297c3a05975e73dbd633d4fb5cbad4a">Enter your game key</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol><h3 id="h_01KBJS5TFMSNQ92YRXTZFS4Y34">&nbsp;</h3><h3 id="h_01KBZKEQQZMNJ3CT8QCQSYABNZ"><a href="https://based.staratlas.com/" rel="noopener">Play-to-Earn with SAGE (Browser Game)</a></h3><p><a href="https://based.staratlas.com/" rel="noopener">SAGE</a> is Star Atlas’ browser-based strategy game built entirely on the Solana blockchain. It’s a <strong>true play-to-earn experience, where you can generate value by exploring the galaxy, mining resources, crafting items, and managing fleets all through on-chain actions</strong></p><p>Here’s what makes <a href="https://based.staratlas.com/" rel="noopener">SAGE</a> unique:</p><ul>
<li class="ck-list-marker-bold" data-list-item-id="e49d129222eadb12f273aa0720b94a95f"><strong>Explore space and discover valuable regions of the Galia Expanse</strong></li>
<li class="ck-list-marker-bold" data-list-item-id="ed1dd585c69240b9f3569938c7c94ce43"><strong>Mine and extract resources like Ore, Carbon, Hydrogen, and more</strong></li>
<li class="ck-list-marker-bold" data-list-item-id="e0f405510fc120ba95919b3852a52ebfb"><strong>Craft materials and components for use in future gameplay</strong></li>
<li class="ck-list-marker-bold" data-list-item-id="e3bd0d1bf78a9c112b1dde9421c582aee"><strong>Earn ATLAS and resources through efficient fleet and economy management</strong></li>
<li data-list-item-id="e4ddfaafa7f8d0211aa0acf95f31ec534">
<a href="https://play.staratlas.com/rentals/" rel="noopener"><strong>List your fleet</strong></a> for rent and earn passive income from other players</li>
</ul><p>To get started in SAGE, you’ll need:</p><ul>
<li data-list-item-id="ec3fce59c5387e3dd08244bf9deaff6ac">A <strong>Solana wallet (e.g. </strong><a href="https://phantom.app" target="_new" rel="noopener"><strong>Phantom</strong></a><strong>)</strong>
</li>
<li data-list-item-id="e38d43640e9a3c13ed62b23143878ac1b">A small amount of <strong>SOL for transaction fees</strong>
</li>
<li class="ck-list-marker-bold" data-list-item-id="e59a57a0ad110bba73bf91fc366d5e5ad">
<strong>ATLAS to buy your first assets on the </strong><a href="https://play.staratlas.com/market" target="_new" rel="noopener"><strong>Star Atlas Marketplace</strong></a>
</li>
<li data-list-item-id="e6eb4bd5e13a668a5f5cb73c984014865">A Ship, a Crew member, and <strong>R4 resources (Fuel, Food, Ammo, Toolkits)</strong>
</li>
</ul><p>You can also <a href="https://play.staratlas.com/rentals/" rel="noopener"><strong>rent a fleet </strong></a>from other players using Fleet Rental if you don’t want to buy ships right away</p><h3 id="h_01KBJS5TFM1RDK2FM376KXDZ96">&nbsp;</h3><h3 id="h_01KBZKEQQZZKMNQWPJC4DRBD33">Other Core Features of Star Atlas</h3><h3 id="h_01KBJRWBBB52J67YV7GBP2B0P1"><a href="https://play.staratlas.com/rentals/" rel="noopener">Fleet Rental</a></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id="efb07745161990c4c4f8d9a161dd786ae">Create a fleet in SAGE and rent it to other players on the Fleet Rental platform for passive income</li></ul><h3 id="h_01KBJS5TFMA2K16Q7RDEBSBWHY"><a href="https://holosim.staratlas.com/" rel="noopener">Free-to-Play Holosim Browser Game</a></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id="ea16f4a2ab62aae9cf41949402a00fbbb">
<a href="https://holosim.staratlas.com/">Holosim</a> is Star Atlas’ Free-to-Play browser-based strategy game built entirely on the Atlasnet blockchain (Solana Fork)</li></ul><h3 id="h_01KBJRWBBB64D17NRB4QRCPSMG"><a href="https://play.staratlas.com/market/" rel="noopener">Galactic Marketplace</a></h3><ul>
<li data-list-item-id="e4f5ea8beb9d03244b24c671995922cdb">Buy and sell ships, crew, resources, claim stakes, collectibles, and more</li>
<li data-list-item-id="eee8a7df372a421cd59ee6a2c8c2532c4">Use ATLAS or USDC to transact</li>
</ul><h3 id="h_01KBJRWBBB50WNCPFV6E7NMTKA"><a href="https://play.staratlas.com/claims/" rel="noopener">Faction Claim</a></h3><p>Stake Claim Stakes to extract R4 resources (Fuel, Food, Ammo, Toolkits) over time. Great for passive income and resource accumulation</p><h3 id="h_01KBJRWBBBC54RR31P4VJBHYPD"><a href="https://play.staratlas.com/dac/" rel="noopener">DACs (Guilds)</a></h3><p>Join or create a <strong>Decentralized Autonomous Corporation (DAC) to play with others, form alliances, and take on big challenges</strong><br><a href="https://play.staratlas.com/dac" target="_new" rel="noopener"><strong>play.staratlas.com/dac</strong></a></p><h3 id="h_01KBJRWBBB3R65EYJGVQHRZ3JJ"><a href="https://govern.staratlas.com/" rel="noopener">Star Atlas DAO</a></h3><ul>
<li data-list-item-id="ee18b5adb6089353e0fb05abbbc87251e">Lock POLIS to gain voting power (PVP) and participate in decentralized proposals that shape the metaverse</li>
<li data-list-item-id="e7a287ec944ab03f6aafa6fd92e3bfa8e">Lock POLIS or ATLAS to earn daily POLIS rewards (higher with POLIS)</li>
<li data-list-item-id="eb65c15ed0e6268964320e94b2ce39b96">Lock ATLAS to reduce fees when trading on the Galactic Marketplace and SAGE’s Local Marketplace</li>
</ul></div>

          

          
        </div>
      </section>

